    "introduction": "Toei's 10th anniversary film. While the story of the Ako Clan's vendetta (Chushingura) hasbeen told countless times, never before has there been a telling with a huge all-star castof this calibre that brings new life to this timeless tale. When Lord Asano is unjustlyexecuted, his loyal retainers strike back for revenge.The tale of 47 Ronin, a true event thathas inspired countless film adaptions, captures the real courage and loyalty of the way ofthe samurai. At a time in japanese history when those qualitys were more myth thanreality, these brave men avenged thier Lord showing tremendous patience and cunning toachieve the ultimate justice.Though they would later be executed for this plan and it's endresults all of japan would remember these men as heroes.This DVD is Digitally Remastered, 16:9 Anamorphic Widescreen, on 2 discs to preservethe stunning razor sharp video quality and brilliant colors, an amazing print of aChushingura classic like you have never seen before. With a most unique pack of DVDExtras; Original Trailers, Movie Photo Gallery, Chushingura Movies Poster Gallery, andmore, 70+ pages of info; \"The 47 Ronin\", \"The Genroku Era\", \"Who is Who?\" (now you canmatch a face with actor/actress names you've seen before), 11 Actor Bios, and 30 minutesof previews from other cool samurai and yakuza movies! A must have disc set!This is NOT the Hawaii TV recording! Remastered from a new amazing print!With removable English Subtitles and DVD Extras.Directed by: MATSUDA SadatsuguCast: KATAOKA Cheizo, NAKAMURA Kinnosuke, SATOMI Kotaro, OKAWA Hashizo,ICHIKAWA Utaemon, KONOE Jushiro, SATOMI Kotaro, AZUMA Chiyonosuke, OTOMORyutaro, OKOCHI Denjiro, TSUKIGATA Ryunosuke, OKA Satomi, OKAWA Keiko, KOGUREMichiyo, CHIHARA Shinobu, YAMAGATA Isao etc.",
